    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽瓦克市长抨击 ICE 在突袭行动开始后拘留陆军退伍军人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/newark-mayor-slams-ice-for-detaining-military-vet-as-raids-start</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽瓦克市市长和该区的一名民主党女议员严厉谴责移民和海关执法局，称执法人员在没有出示搜查令的情况下突击检查了新泽西州的一家企业并拘留了无证居民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/newark-mayor-slams-ice-for-detaining-military-vet-as-raids-start</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 00:45:25 GMT</pubDate>
